00:04:21.700 --> 00:04:22.800
Tout est flou.

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:25.460
Vous me suivez ?

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:27.980
Oui, je comprends.

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:31.780
